[SHORT DESC]
30% chance to lower target's accuracy by 1 stage.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 30% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Mud Bomb has little competitive use, as it is weak and inaccurate. The chance to lower accuracy is also not a big draw, since doing so is an unreliable tactic. Mud Bomb is eclipsed by Earth Power, which is both more powerful and more accurate.</p>
 
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/earth_power">Earth Power</a> is a more powerful option.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/mirror_shot">Mirror Shot</a> is a Steel-type equivalent.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/octazooka">Octazooka</a> is a Water-type equivalent.</p>